### POST /api/v1/auth/refresh
### Descripción: Refrescar token usando refreshToken. Devuelve nuevo accessToken y refreshToken.
### Headers requeridos: ninguno.
### Códigos: 200 OK (LoginResponse) | 401 { "error", "code" }

# @name refresh
POST {{BASE_URL}}/api/v1/auth/refresh
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "refreshToken": "{{REFRESH_TOKEN}}"
}

### Response esperado (200):
# {
#   "accessToken": "eyJ...",
#   "refreshToken": "string",
#   "accessTokenExpiresAtUtc": "2025-03-02T12:00:00Z",
#   "expiresInSeconds": 3600
# }

### Response error (401):
# {
#   "error": "string",
#   "code": "string"
# }
